}}\pard{\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx8640\tx7920 \qj\li0\fi0\ri0\sb0\sl\sa0 \plain\f2\fs22\cf0\ul \par
\qj\li0\fi0\ri0\sb0\sl\sa0 \plain\f2\fs22\cf0 \par
